The musicians who performed on "Isn<U+2019>t It a Pity" are believed to be as follows:<ref name=autogenerated1 /><ref name="The_Beatles_Bible">[http://www.beatlesbible.com/people/george-harrison/songs/isnt-it-a-pity/ George Harrison: Isn't It a Pity], The Beatles Bible (retrieved 17 November 2011).</ref><ref name="Spizer p 212" />

