*[[Tom Evans (musician)|Tom Evans]] <U+2013> acoustic guitar
*[[Joey Molland]] <U+2013> acoustic guitar
*[[Klaus Voormann]] <U+2013> bass
*[[Ringo Starr]] <U+2013> drums
*[[Mike Gibbins]] <U+2013> tambourine
*[[John Barham]] <U+2013> orchestral and choral arrangements
*''uncredited/player not known'' <U+2013> [[maracas]]

